To use the grounder, you need to first install

1) Pypy3

2) gringo (see https://potassco.org/)

3) the asp-grounding-planning repo (https://github.com/abcorrea/asp-grounding-planning)
   - follow the instructions there to set up the environment variables

4) add an environment variable $COUNT_GROUND_ACTIONS_BIN_PATH pointing to the
   script "count-ground-actions.py" in the repository of step (2)

To build Fast Downward, follow the instructions at https://www.fast-downward.org/
